title: Case Logic CDW-32 32 Capacity Classic CD Wallet (Black)
description: Case Logic is obsessed with organization! No matter who you are, what toys, tools or technology you have, where you are, or where you are going, Case Logic is your partner in managing the things that matter to you. We are the "stuff wranglers" that make life easier. The Caselogic CDW-32 32 Capacity Classic CD Wallet holds 32 CDs or 16 with liner notes. Patented ProSleeves provide ultra protection by keeping dirt away to prevent scratching of delicate CD surfaces. Durable padded outer-material resistant to heat, moisture and tearing. 25 Year Warranty!
